    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. Not a single scratch, dent, or speck of dust to be found! It drives just as smoothly as the day I bought it, and it still has that fresh car smell. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take a look!",
