    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the zenith of the analog driving experience, featuring the highly sought-after 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six engine and a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle is in concours condition, with a flawless DME report and zero bore scoring concerns. It comes equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal lateral grip and chassis composure. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, the engine bay is pristine, and the underbody remains showroom-dry with no fluid seepage or bushing fatigue. A truly investment-grade example for the purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
