    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the term 'pristine.' This one-owner masterpiece has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since the day it left the showroom. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating that makes the paint glow under any lighting. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, still carrying that distinct new-car scent, while every technological feature and button functions with factory precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history exclusively performed by certified master technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, high-performance rubber, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning driver to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
      "price": 48750.0,
