    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom-level condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, so you\u2019re getting flawless paint, a spotless interior, and a drive that\u2019s smooth as silk. It\u2019s been garage-kept and meticulously loved, and it\u2019s just waiting for its next adventure. Come give it a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
