    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S, a superlative example of the 997.1 generation. This vehicle features the 3.8L flat-six power plant, delivering a linear torque curve and high-revving performance through a traditional 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) provides precision damping, while the braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers for exceptional thermal dissipation. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of fluid seepage or bushing fatigue. With a factory-spec limited-slip differential and a documented service history addressing the IMS and bore-scoring concerns, this chassis remains as rigid and responsive as the day it left Zuffenhausen.",
